&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;text-decoration: underline;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;ROLES SPECIFIC OUTCOMES&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;External Communications&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br&gt;Processes speaker and resource requests, and corresponds with key student, supporter, and donor audiences for virtual and in-person events across the United States.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
